'''Adolphe Nshimirimana''' (12 Nzeri 1964 - 2 Kanama 2015) yari umujenerali w’ingabo z’[[Uburundi]]  wabaye umuyobozi mukuru w’ingabo , ndetse akaba n'umujanama mukuru wa perezida ushinzwe umutekano mu gihugu ndetse akaba n'umufasha wa politiki wa perezida Pierre Nkurunziza .  zabonye Lt. Nshimirimana nk'umuyobozi ushinzwe umutekano mu gihugu Nkurunziza ''nk'umuyobozi'' w'ikigo c'igihugu gishinzwe iperereza .  Yavukiye i Nyabiraba muri Komine ya Gishubi , Intara ya Gitega.<ref>https://alchetron.com/Adolphe-Nshimirimana</ref> 
