Mu mwaka wa 2015, Perezida Pierre Nkurunziza yatangaje ko ashaka manda ya gatatu, bituma abantu benshi batavuga rumwe nubutegetsi bagira imyiyerekano yo kwiyamiriza ikiringo ca 3 . 

'''Adolphe Nshimirimana'''  yafashije gutsinda umugambi wo guhirika ubutegetsi bwa Nkurunziza muri Rusama 2015 kandi yabona ko ari we wateguye igitero co guhasha abigaragamvya.  

Umuryango uharanira uburenganzira bwa muntu washinja Nshimirimana kuba "umwe mu bantu bakomeye ba perezida."  Nshimirimana yagize uruhara runini mu gihe imyigaragamvyo  yo kugwanya Nkurunziza vyakomeje hagati muri 2015. 


Nk’uko Carina Tertsakian wo muri Human Rights Watch abivuga, "Nubwoankewa kubera izina iweye ry'ubugome, Adolphe yaboga ko adakoraho, nta muntu n'umwe wari ufite ubutwari bwo gutinyuka,ankewa ngo amutange ibitekerezo, ngo abimubaze.. Ariko, amaherezo yaje kwicwa nabawan a Nkurunziza.

Igenekerezo rya 4/12/ 2015, Nkurunziza yategetse abapolisi gushaka abicanyi ba Nshimirimana, mu minsi icumi bari bahagarariwe nk'umuntu w’iburyo bwa perezida. Mukwumunani 2015. Nshimirimana yarapfuye abandi batatu barakomere bikabije .

Igenekerezo rya 13/12/ 2016, abapolisi bo mu Burundi batangaje ko umwe mu bakekwaho kuba barishe Nshimirimana yatorotse gereza yica umuzamu.
